title: My keyboard is not registering The letters I am trying to touch. Anybody else having this issue?
content: My keyboard is not correctly identifying the letters I am trying to touch on the screen. Is anybody else having this issue? I have tried restarting my phone, powering it off and on, and putting it in safe mode. None of this has worked. I am needing to talk to text in order to correctly type what I want to type.
